data.description: Rare find for all Military personnel, VA assumable rate at 5.75%! Welcome to this exquisite fully remodeled two-bedroom, two-bath condo located in the heart of East Village, downtown San Diego. Boasting an oversized layout, this spacious residence is ideally situated just blocks away from the excitement of PETCO Park, the vibrant Gaslamp Quarter, and some amazing new coffee shops. The interior of this condo has been thoughtfully upgraded to offer a modern and stylish living experience. Gleaming waterproof floors throughout the unit add a touch of elegance and practicality, while stainless steel appliances in the fully equipped kitchen make meal preparation a breeze. The open concept living and dining area features custom canned lighting that illuminates the space beautifully. Additionally, the condo comes with a full-size washer and dryer for added convenience along with all new stainless steel appliances, newly painted walls, and life time carpet in the bedrooms. For your peace of mind, the unit also comes with a secure underground parking spot and a dedicated storage locker in the garage. The primary suite is a retreat of its own, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and a private full remodeled bath. The second bedroom, thoughtfully placed on the opposite side of the primary suite, offers privacy and versatility. This condo truly provides the best of downtown living with its proximity to entertainment and dining options, while also offering a comfortable and contemporary living space for its lucky new owner.
